{"TopicId":173963,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"RIP R. Lee Ermey","CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T13:59:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T13:59:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRIP, Sir~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.nytimes.com/2018/04/15/obituaries/r-lee-ermey-dead-actor.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.nytimes.com/2018/04/15/obituaries/r-lee-ermey-dead-actor.html\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSaint","CreatedById":70033,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T15:25:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was a Marine, which is an honorific that requires no embellishment. And he was a fine man, one who passed through even Hollywood uncorrupted. Until Valhalla, Gunny.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Genolution","CreatedById":54840,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T21:00:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn American treasure. For this loss we are all poorer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-16T21:30:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-17T08:24:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was the technical advisor on \u0022Full Metal Jacket\u0022, until Kubrick saw him trying to coach the actor they had hired for the role.\u00A0 Kubrick decided Emery would play the part much better, and so started his acting career.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe will be missed.\u00A0\u00A0 Giant bucket of win.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nuke","CreatedById":10883,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-17T10:27:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsiege at firebase gloria is one of my favorite war movies. gunny will be missed. o7 semper fi.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}